1. Install remote-container VS code extension.
2. Install docker.
3. Clone repo. https://github.com/ptoner/large
4. Edit .devcontainer\devcontainer.json
5. Change path on line 11 to be a folder that actually exists for you.
6. Click on green button in bottom left corner
    -> Open folder in container
7. It'll create the docker VM and launch it. Hopefully.
8. Open terminal ->
    ganache-cli 
9. Open another terminal ->
    Copy .devcontainer/start.sh 
    Paste into terminal 
10. Open another terminal ->
    npm run watch
11. Open another terminal ->
    npm run serve
12. Forward port 4001 
13. Forward port 5001 
14. Forward port 8080
15. Forward port 8081
16. Forward port 8545